      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Method of manufactured solutions (MMS) applied to Navier-Stokes solver and hemolysis transport equation; observed order of accuracy within 10% of formal order.",
      "rationale": "MMS verification performed for incompressible Navier-Stokes equations; observed order 1.92 vs. formal order 2.0 (4% deviation). MMS not performed for the hemolysis power-law transport equation; that subroutine verified only against analytic solutions for simplified 1D cases. Gap in 3D hemolysis transport verification limits achieved level to 3."
    },
