      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic centrifugal pump, same geometry as COU. Operating range covers 3–6 L/min; COU requires 2.5–7 L/min, leaving extrapolation at boundaries. Pulsatile conditions absent from validation campaign. Blood formulation (porcine) differs from clinical human blood. Achieved level 2 vs. required 5 represents the largest credibility gap."
    },
